graph TB
    subgraph "Device - Your Phone"
        subgraph "UI Layer (XML + ViewBinding)"
            MA[MainActivity<br/>Home Screen]
            GLA[GroceryListActivity<br/>Grocery List Screen]
            SA[SettingsActivity<br/>Settings Screen]
            GA[GroceryAdapter<br/>RecyclerView Adapter]
        end

        VM[GroceryViewModel<br/>Business Logic & State]
        REPO[GroceryRepository<br/>Data Abstraction Layer]

        subgraph "Room Database (SQLite)"
            DAO[GroceryDao<br/>CRUD Operations]
            ROOM[(Room Database<br/>Local Storage)]
            E1[GroceryItem Entity<br/>id: Int, name: String, isChecked: Boolean]
        end
    end

    GLA -->|User Actions| VM
    VM -->|Observe State<br/>LiveData/Flow| GLA
    GLA -->|Binds Items| GA

    VM <-->|Get/Update Data| REPO

    REPO <-->|CRUD via DAOs| DAO
    DAO <-->|SQL Queries| ROOM
    ROOM -.->|Stores| E1

